On October 30, 2020, mannitol was approved by the FDA as add-on maintenance therapy for the control of pulmonary symptoms associated with cystic fibrosis in adult patients and is currently marketed for this indication under the name BRONCHITOL® by Chiesi USA Inc.[L20024]', '["B05CX04", "A06AD16", "R05CB16", "B05BC01", "V04CX04"]', '[]');
